nodes.title: Input: Manual Prompt
widgets_values: A beautiful young woman with colorful rainbow braided hair in a high bun, blue eyes, wearing a white sleeveless top. She is in a bedroom with a gold clock on the wall, a bookshelf with books, and a red teddy bear in the background. Motion: She is dancing to the rhythm, swaying her body and shoulders, moving her arms gently, smiling at the camera. Dynamic movement, fluid motion, high quality, 4k.

--- ESPAOL: MANUAL DE USO (EDICIN FERNANDO) ---

ENTORNO:

 Probado y Optimizado en: RunningHub.

Advertencia: En otras plataformas o PC local, verifica tener el modelo Wan 2.2 y suficiente VRAM.

1. CALIDAD Y RESOLUCIN (Nodo #340)

Busca el nodo pequeo #340 (easy int) conectado al panel central.

480: Modo Rpido (Borrador).

720: Modo HD (Recomendado).

1080: Full HD (Riesgo alto de error).

2. REGLAS DEL PROMPT (Nodo #73)

Escribe manualmente en el cuadro verde de la izquierda.

Parte 1 (Sujeto): Describe EXACTAMENTE la foto.

Parte 2 (Movimiento): Ordena la accin.

Nota: Ignora el Nodo #213 (Dragon), est desactivado.

3.  ADVERTENCIA: NODOS "FANTASMA" (NO BORRAR)

Hay nodos que parecen desconectados/sueltos.

NO LOS BORRES! Se conectan inalmbricamente ("WiFi") para transmitir datos internos. Si los quitas, el flujo fallar.

4. CMO GUARDAR (Nodo #226)

Clic Derecho sobre el video > "Save Image".

--- ENGLISH: USER MANUAL (FERNANDO EDITION) ---

ENVIRONMENT:

 Tested & Optimized on: RunningHub.

1. QUALITY & RESOLUTION (Node #340)

Find node #340 (easy int).

480: Speed Mode.

720: HD Mode (Recommended).

1080: Full HD (High risk).

2. PROMPT RULES (Node #73)

Type in the green box on the left.

Part 1 (Subject): Describe EXACTLY what you see.

Part 2 (Motion): Command the action.

3.  WARNING: "GHOST" NODES (DO NOT DELETE)

Some nodes appear disconnected or floating.

DO NOT DELETE THEM! They connect wirelessly to transmit data. Removing them will break the workflow.

4. HOW TO SAVE (Node #226)

Right-Click on video > "Save Image".
